subject: Football
Pro Bowl
lead_paragraph: Few moved very fast, no one flattened a quarterback and there were no bone-jarring hits in Team Irvin’s 32-28 victory over Team Carter during Sunday’s Pro Bowl in Glendale, Ariz.
